                            <h4><span style="color: #0080ff; font-size: large;"><strong>Quivers Ecommerce Program Information</strong></span></h4>
                                <p>Alpha Professional Tools<sup>&reg;</sup> was founded in 1986 and has become a leading manufacturer of quality tools for professionals in the natural/engineered stone, porcelain, ceramic, glass, construction, marine and automotive industries. Alpha<sup>&reg;</sup> provides the best products for cutting, drilling, shaping and polishing all types of materials.</p>
                                <p>Although Alpha<sup>&reg;</sup> products are sold via our distributor network, we now offer a place to order online for quick delivery from one of our authorized distributors. Through this service, stocking distributors process orders for customers near them to get the product shipped as quick as possible.</p>
                                <p>To utilize this service, simply go to the desired product page and select the <strong>"BUY NOW"</strong> tab.  Enter the quantity desired and click Add To Cart.  Once checkout is complete, the order will then be processed and fulfilled by an Alpha<sup>&reg;</sup> distributor.</p>
